          <br />
          towering pines, beside a shimmering lake, or on the edge of a <br />
          windswept canyon, these sites invite adventurers to unplug, breathe
          <br />
          fresh air, and reconnect with the simple joys of outdoor living.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/campgrounds"
          class="btn btn-secondary font-weight-bold btn-lg bg-white"
